        {
            "title": "緬甸詐騙園區｜總理佩通坦指7000人獲救  待轉移至泰國",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"緬甸詐騙園區7000人獲救待轉移至泰國。（路透社）\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/647a416a71bf993dd434dbc63331319f/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250219/_2025021913440536854.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">緬甸詐騙園區7000人獲救待轉移至泰國。（路透社）</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>泰國總理佩通坦（Paetongtarn Shinawatra）周三（19日）表示，從緬甸詐騙園區獲救的約7000人正等待轉移至泰國。她表示，泰國政府正迅速採取行動。\n\n</p><h2>東南亞多國合力打擊</h2>\n<p>緬甸、泰國、老撾、馬來西亞等東南亞國家近期採取斷電斷網、加強立法、執法等多項措施，嚴厲打擊電訊詐騙和網絡賭博等跨境犯罪活動。多國表示將持續加強東南亞國家協會內部及與中國等國家合作，加強對違法犯罪集團的聯合打擊。\n\n</p>\n<p><strong>相關新聞：<a href=\"https://www.stheadline.com/realtime-world/3429875/%E7%B7%AC%E7%94%B8%E8%A9%90%E9%A8%99%E5%9C%92%E5%8D%80%E4%B8%AD%E7%B7%AC%E6%B3%B0%E5%90%88%E4%BD%9C%E9%87%8D%E6%93%8A-%E5%A6%99%E7%93%A6%E5%BA%95%E4%B8%80%E5%A4%A9273%E9%9D%9E%E6%B3%95%E5%85%A5%E5%A2%83%E8%80%85%E8%A2%AB%E6%8D%95\">緬甸詐騙園區｜中緬泰合作重擊 妙瓦底一天273非法入境者被捕</a></strong>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"泰國停止向緬甸妙瓦底供電。（新華社）\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/b42e6973b0aa493e12345333fed9bd9d/2025-02/19022025_064_XH.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        泰國停止向緬甸妙瓦底供電。（新華社）\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"緬甸KK園區惡名昭彰。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/cc0607fc9d6422c5871dafc10e99646e/2025-02/19022025_063.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        緬甸KK園區惡名昭彰。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<p>泰國《曼谷郵報》周一（17日）報道，過去三周，緬甸軍方對妙瓦底等地的電騙中心實施清剿行動，旨在分階段驅逐電騙園區約1萬名外籍人士。\n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
